 When I recovered my seats, I used the modern equivalent of the=20
reclaimed fiber pads called batting, from the sewing and craft store.
This is the white fibrous stuff that comes in a roll. I sprayed a thin
layer of 3M brand spray adhesive on the horse hair pads to keep=20
the batting in place while I slid on the vinyl covers.
I am very happy with the result, and would recommend it.

Jako

70' Kombi, pogo stick, rotary nose hair trimmer. =20

